{"tid":1463502,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家明唔明政治某程度黎講係同sales一樣 入黎聽下我講","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:24:01.000Z","uid":150086,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31099f94719930330248cc0da02a9d125c5f8424","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"我知道由6月到依加香港人創造左好多奇蹟，但係要記住仲係有好多人未必咁認同同埋對香港局勢有興趣，而要將我地理念傳開去，<strong>就好似sales一樣野比人咁</strong> 依次機場一戰都係咁 要識包裝，你諗下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻人上機</span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">癱瘓機場</span>其實係一樣，但點解癱瘓機場個名好聽咁多容易俾人接受？我地要識包裝比人睇同自己人睇，香港人係因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太多人入機場和平集會而導致機場交通癱瘓</span>而唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋主動阻住人上機</span> 同一樣結果 不過可以將個焦點同責任推比政府 而唔係我地受晒批評同埋負面影象，記住我地形象係受到壓迫嘅弱小一群！最後，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"a48e0f1d2eab404ad5464daf4fdda328bfcca5b5","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"3c9b7e3b66b5d9d8f5e373306158fd0d898c020f","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"883a8e89d2bad6e850068b0ba4ecd3b6de57fcae","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:13:51.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a848f8f0390c96aeeea78a7059aaf0b87d06cbed","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0e6c8985889d81865228a46c8c3bdee6fe60ad58","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ca800e546f334ec7f92153ed64a2684f83e0f705","tid":1463502,"uid":150086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b7c85c75a1e250e8c7947e4ac3a4eb0906c3694b","tid"